oai_dc:dc.dc:title: View of Tennessee Capitol from Bicentennial Mall State Park
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Color photograph of a view of the Tennessee State Capitol and other buildings from Bicentennial Mall State Park. The central emblem of the Tennessee flag is visible on the lawn. Features a divided back, narrative, and a semi-transparent logo for the state park on reverse. [No. 327610]
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Tennessee State Photographic Services
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: State parks & reserves; Capitols; Buildings
